*******************Model View Controller*********************

1. DispatcherServlet : The entry / configuration point for the Application
2. Controller : Command Pattern object that handles the request and determines which vie to route to
3. Request Mapping : The URL and requst type that a method is tied to
4. View Resolver : Used to locate JSP page or whatever view we are using
5. Servlet-config : Configuration file per DispatcherServlet 


